rows.label: qst200401_msg0001
rows.name:
Come on, Ellenora!
Time to pay up!

rows.label: qst200401_msg0002
rows.name:
I-I'm sorry, but I'll
need another day or two...

rows.label: qst200401_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm gettin' awful tired
of hearin' that line.

rows.label: qst200401_msg0004
rows.name:
How long're you gonna
keep us waitin'? Huh?

rows.label: qst200401_msg0005
rows.name:
B-but I don't have the money...
Please, just give me time...

rows.label: qst200401_msg0006
rows.name:
Yeah, no.
Your time's already up.

rows.label: qst200401_msg0007
rows.name:
If she can't pay, she can't pay.
Hey, I've got an idea...

rows.label: qst200401_msg0009
rows.name:
Yeah, we can't let them
get away with this...

rows.label: qst200401_msg0013
rows.name: I do as I please, gutter trash!

rows.label: qst200401_msg0015
rows.name:
H-h-he's strong all right...
We're outmatched here...

rows.label: qst200401_msg0016
rows.name:
I say again: leave.
I will not repeat myself further...
